cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper involves the use of deep reinforcement learning for optimizing runtime parameters of cloud databases, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also deals with database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) in the context of optimizing performance metrics. The paper also discusses the use of asynchronous experience management, which is related to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the use of normalized advantage functions is a common technique in reinforcement learning (cs.NE).
